+- [ ] This PR references a real issue above (require-issue.yml)
+- [ ] `cargo xtask ci` passes locally (skip if docs-only) — fmt, clippy, build, test, deny, conformance
+- [ ] If the networked data path is affected, `cargo xtask integration` passes (needs Docker)
